Author: sewnp
Text: Hi, I've had my eating disorder for 11 years. I say this because I want you to feel less alone with your struggle. I also have EDNoS so I often struggle with worrying that I'm not sick enough to matter. However, this is completely not true and only our illness ridden brains being cruel to ourselves. Take care, everyone in this community has similar worries and concerns.

Author: coffinOfcans
Text: You are not alone fellow sufferer. We all share similar if not the same symptoms of this horrible disorder. You are NEVER alone and you are welcome here ðŸ’œ
